d":454294,"uid":131332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樣問緊自己呢個問題<br />\n屋企唔等錢洗 自己物質慾望又唔太強<br />\n真係唔知返黎為乜</blockquote><br />\n學我，上星期quit 左30k/month 嘅工去流浪"},{"pid":"96f0cf4b77a39aec3c2e91b64498a45613983292","tid":454294,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"為左同啲同事勾心鬥角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981bbf1346cda969f57244ff8ee841b262e6d531","tid":454294,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>錢 no doubt</blockquote><br />\n無哂自己時間好唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要分清楚<br />\n生存 =/= 生活<br />\n冇錢生存唔到<br />\n生存都成問題如何談得上生活</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點定義生存先，食得飽就夠嘅話，其實香港應該唔難生存，但你話要買樓有自己住所先叫生存嘅話，咁你呢世都無生活過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己定義既生存係講緊基本衣食住行<br />\n你正正常常有份正職都應該申請唔到政府樓<br />\n同屋企人住都要比家用 自己住都要比錢租<br />\n衣服乾乾淨淨合身舒適<br />\n三餐食得溫飽<br />\n行就唔係講旅行果D, 真係講緊基本出出入入車費 (返工之類)<br />\n生存講緊好基本既野 已經將娛樂拋開"},{"pid":"fb90191df6c4045af6a8218fb05b65f8e070d4b4","tid":454294,"uid":32187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"有冇人搵到份好岩自己做既工每日都好想/有動力返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ccf705fee1a16086cbdfdab984d824fe81078d","tid":454294,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人搵到份好岩自己做既工每日都好想/有動力返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊依個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"